<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Feedback on Waste Collection - Waste Zero</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #888888;
            padding: 20px 0;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Thank You for Your Feedback!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>We appreciate your feedback regarding your recent waste collection service.</p>

            <div class="highlight">
                <p><strong>Your Rating:</strong> <%= rating %> out of 5</p>
                <p><strong>Your Comment:</strong> <%= comment %></p>
            </div>

            <p>Your insights help us improve our services and provide better experiences for our customers.</p>
            <p>If you have any further questions or concerns, please do not hesitate to reach out to us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
